SETUP
------
1. Install dependencies:
     sudo gem install hpricot htmlentities will_paginate
2. Migrate the database
     rake db:migrate:reset
3. Call Site class methods to start crawling
     script/runner -e development "Site.update_all"
4. Start server. If you have newer Rails, force start with Webrick
     ./script/server webrick
5. Try it out in your browser http://localhost:3000

NOTES
-------
1. Not tested with Phusion Passenger.
2. Rails 2.1 is frozen in.
3. Default Site records created during migration.

